{"tid":1532692,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"雙grp奇謀-樹窿&DSE學術支援(再post)","createTime":"2019-09-02T14:57:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T19:03:45.000Z","uid":244876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b86dcc852d99fff8781f718a3e9f58ac2bfcccf7","tid":1532692,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:57:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去兩個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依兩個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1audFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=4d03aa65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外就係<br />\n過去個兩個月正正常常係比應屆DSE同學仔溫書休息既<br />\n可惜呢個政府搞到大家奉獻左成個暑假，為左自己又好，為左將來又好，為左下一代又好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前有見連登上有多個關於網上問功課谷既需求，有見及此就有呢個DSE支援服務。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，免費網上問功課谷一直以唔張揚嘅方法存在。谷內有十多位Tutors (當中包括現職老師及名校畢業生在讀生)同DSE同學仔。形式係以分科細谷你問我答為主，亦有提供簡單練習同改文服務。同學亦可以問升學選科等問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一直隱姓埋名係為左保障學生安全。但見到需求增加，又多左好多不同既補習post。所以我地希望提供俾同學多一個安全安心既選擇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如有同學有需要，請聯絡：<br />\nTG: mama612 <br />\nTG: UuuncleK<br />\n(暫時有足夠Tutor所以暫不接受更多tutor)<br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2c94cf23680f57c178e7b70217693b7c4b422f","tid":1532692,"uid":120412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:59:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"59611b0738c19fb01b547eb1bf1fa6569f98f193","tid":1532692,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:05:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bdb51808c61aae6edf50f90e6d2512c7f5ab8a1b","tid":1532692,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:08:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"961f770113685a44a4e680b13f2255efd2067b03","tid":1532692,"uid":266362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:11:07.000Z","msg":"跪求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">想大個仔獨立必睇</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">召喚攬炒巴及歷史法師！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></span></span>遇怪魔想變大個，就一定一定要睇！<br />\n<br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg